{
  "stem": "1641.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he said-- we were just guessing what he said, but he must have said, where are these Jews going?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What's up?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Where are you going?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Well, the Hungarian said, well, they are doing labor service.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They're going to dig trenches against the-- to-- you know, to defend the country against the advancing Russians.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the two officers were German Gestapo officers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they said to them, well, never mind your train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You just tell your men to follow-- follow us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then there were six German behind us, another six in front of us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they're leading us through the town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The town's name was Nagyvarad-- N-A-G-Y-V-A-R-A-D.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's a big-- fairly big town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't know where we are going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had no idea what he wants or what it is.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we walked through the town, and eventually we got to the walls of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we have to go through the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then-- then we knew where we are.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then we were in the Nagyvarad ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was 32,000 people inside, pressed together in a couple of streets, about 15 people in each room, and-- well, yeah, about 60, 70 in each flat.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were inside the ghetto, and that was that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then all-- all sorts of rumors went around in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The rumors-- they ranged from the-- the most optimistic was that Germany needs us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They would-- they would probably use us for labor, working in German factories.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The older people-- of course, they couldn't do any work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, they-- we guessed that they might be put in special concentration camps or something like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was all just guess.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Other thing which happened in the ghetto-- the food was very bad.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
